{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775900803477,"sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","part":{"id":"prt_d7befbc7c001wJ4jV73DExgaof","messageID":"msg_d7befa450001ubbKcqXmxEdqHw","sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-5ac1b22c21f444d28bda3ed99b2f9d5e","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043 Implementation Notes\n2: \n3: ## Implementation Status\n4: - [ ] Spec definition\n5: - [ ] Architecture design documentation\n6: - [ ] API documentation\n7: - [ ] Documentation\n8: \n9: ## Implementation Details\n10: \n11: ### Files Created\n12: \n13: [To be filled during implementation]\n14: \n15: ### Notes\n16: \n17: [To be filled during implementation]\n\n(End of file - total 17 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043 Implementation Notes\n\n## Implementation Status\n- [ ] Spec definition\n- [ ] Architecture design documentation\n- [ ] API documentation\n- [ ] Documentation\n\n## Implementation Details\n\n### Files Created\n\n[To be filled during implementation]\n\n### Notes\n\n[To be filled during implementation]","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/README.md","time":{"start":1775900803447,"end":1775900803476}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775900803479,"sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","part":{"id":"prt_d7befc164001P8CWTdhwp7K36t","messageID":"msg_d7befa450001ubbKcqXmxEdqHw","sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-dbbc60cb72274bd79ab0c7b166a01798","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: 本提案旨在完善和增强 AgentCube 平台的架构设计文档与 API 文档，为开发者、运维人员和用户提供全面、准确、易于理解的技术文档。这将包括架构概览、模块设计、数据流、API 规范、部署指南等内容，并建立文档维护和更新机制。\n6: \n7: ## Purpose\n8: \n9: 为 AgentCube 平台建立完整、系统化的技术文档体系，实现以下目标：\n10: \n11: 1. **知识传递与共享**：为团队成员提供统一的技术知识库，加速新成员上手\n12: 2. **降低沟通成本**：通过详细的文档减少重复的技术问题解答\n13: 3. **提升开发效率**：为 API 使用和系统集成提供清晰的参考\n14: 4. **支持运维部署**：提供部署、配置、监控和故障排查指南\n15: 5. **促进社区发展**：为开源社区提供高质量的用户和开发者文档\n16: 6. **确保文档可持续性**：建立文档维护和更新流程\n17: \n18: ## Module\n19: \n20: `docs`\n21: \n22: ## Language\n23: \n24: Markdown\n25: \n26: ## Size\n27: \n28: M\n29: \n30: ## Scope\n31: \n32: ### In Scope\n33: \n34: #### 架构设计文档\n35: \n36: 1. **架构概览** (`docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`)\n37:    - 系统整体架构图\n38:    - 核心组件介绍\n39:    - 技术栈说明\n40:    - 设计原则和架构决策\n41: \n42: 2. **模块设计** (`docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`)\n43:    - Router 模块详细设计\n44:    - Store 模块详细设计\n45:    - Workload Manager 模块详细设计\n46:    - PicoD 模块详细设计\n47:    - Controller Manager 模块详细设计\n48:    - Agentd 模块详细设计\n49:    - 模块间通信协议\n50: \n51: 3. **数据流** (`docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md`)\n52:    - 请求处理流程\n53:    - 会话生命周期\n54:    - 数据流转图\n55:    - 状态机设计\n56: \n57: 4. **安全架构** (`docs/docs/architecture/security.md`)\n58:    - 认证和授权机制\n59:    - 网络隔离策略\n60:    - 资源隔离机制\n61:    - 数据加密方案\n62: \n63: 5. **可观测性** (`docs/docs/architecture/observability.md`)\n64:    - 监控指标设计\n65:    - 日志规范\n66:    - 分布式追踪\n67:    - 告警策略\n68: \n69: #### API 文档\n70: \n71: 1. **API 总览** (`docs/docs/api/overview.md`)\n72:    - API 版本策略\n73:    - 认证方式\n74:    - 通用响应格式\n75:    - 错误码定义\n76: \n77: 2. **REST API** (`docs/docs/api/rest.md`)\n78:    - 会话管理 API\n79:    - 资源代理 API\n80:    - 代码执行 API\n81:    - 文件操作 API\n82:    - 健康检查 API\n83: \n84: 3. **gRPC API** (`docs/docs/api/grpc.md`)\n85:    - gRPC 服务定义\n86:    - 消息类型\n87:    - 流式接口\n88:    - 错误处理\n89: \n90: 4. **CRD API** (`docs/docs/api/crd.md`)\n91:    - AgentRuntime CRD 规范\n92:    - CodeInterpreter CRD 规范\n93:    - 状态字段说明\n94:    - 条件类型定义\n95: \n96: 5. **SDK 参考** (`docs/docs/api/sdk.md`)\n97:    - Python SDK 文档\n98:    - Go client 文档\n99:    - CLI 工具文档\n100:    - 代码示例\n101: \n102: #### 部署和运维文档\n103: \n104: 1. **部署指南** (`docs/docs/deployment/overview.md`)\n105:    - 部署架构\n106:    - 前置条件\n107:    - 安装步骤\n108:    - 配置说明\n109: \n110: 2. **Kubernetes 部署** (`docs/docs/deployment/kubernetes.md`)\n111:    - Helm Chart 使用\n112:    - 手动部署步骤\n113:    - 配置参数说明\n114:    - 升级和回滚\n115: \n116: 3. **监控和告警** (`docs/docs/operations/monitoring.md`)\n117:    - 监控指标\n118:    - Prometheus 配置\n119:    - Grafana 面板\n120:    - 告警规则\n121: \n122: 4. **故障排查** (`docs/docs/operations/troubleshooting.md`)\n123:    - 常见问题\n124:    - 日志分析\n125:    - 性能调优\n126:    - 应急处理\n127: \n128: #### 用户指南\n129: \n130: 1. **快速开始** (`docs/docs/introduction/quickstart.md`)\n131:    - 环境准备\n132:    - 快速安装\n133:    - 第一个示例\n134:    - 下一步\n135: \n136: 2. **教程** (`docs/docs/tutorials/`)\n137:    - 基础教程\n138:    - 高级用法\n139:    - 集成示例\n140:    - 最佳实践\n141: \n142: ### Out of Scope\n143: \n144: - 产品营销文档（产品功能介绍、优势对比等）\n145: - 商业文档（定价、SLA、许可证等）\n146: - 第三方集成文档（特定云厂商的详细集成指南）\n147: - 多语言翻译（仅提供英文文档）\n148: - 视频教程和多媒体内容\n149: - 交互式 API 测试工具\n150: \n151: ## Impact Analysis\n152: \n153: ### Positive Impacts\n154: \n155: 1. **知识管理**\n156:    - 建立集中的技术知识库\n157:    - 减少知识流失风险\n158:    - 提升团队协作效率\n159: \n160: 2. **开发效率**\n161:    - 减少 API 查询时间\n162:    - 降低集成开发难度\n163:    - 加速问题排查过程\n164: \n165: 3. **用户体验**\n166:    - 提供清晰的使用指南\n167:    - 减少用户学习曲线\n168:    - 提升用户满意度\n169: \n170: 4. **社区发展**\n171:    - 吸引更多开发者参与\n172:    - 降低贡献门槛\n173:    - 提升项目专业性\n174: \n175: 5. **运维支持**\n176:    - 标准化部署流程\n177:    - 快速定位问题\n178:    - 减少运维成本\n179: \n180: ### Negative Impacts\n181: \n182: 1. **开发资源投入**\n183:    - 需要投入专门的文档编写时间（估计 80-120 小时）\n184:    - 可能延迟部分功能开发进度\n185:    - 需要持续维护和更新\n186: \n187: 2. **文档同步挑战**\n188:    - API 变更时需要同步更新文档\n189:    - 可能出现文档与代码不一致的情况\n190:    - 需要建立文档审查流程\n191: \n192: 3. **学习成本**\n193:    - 新的文档框架和规范需要团队学习\n194:    - 文档工具链需要配置和熟悉\n195: \n196: ### Risk Mitigation\n197: \n198: 1. **资源投入**\n199:    - 将文档工作纳入开发任务，分配专门的开发时间\n200:    - 采用文档驱动开发（DDD）方法，在开发功能时同步编写文档\n201:    - 优先完善核心模块文档，逐步扩展到完整覆盖\n202: \n203: 2. **文档同步**\n204:    - 在 CI/CD 流程中加入文档生成和验证步骤\n205:    - 使用 OpenAPI/Swagger 自动生成 API 文档\n206:    - 建立代码变更时必须更新对应文档的规范\n207:    - 定期进行文档审计和更新\n208: \n209: 3. **学习成本**\n210:    - 选择成熟、易用的文档工具（如 Docusaurus、MkDocs）\n211:    - 编写文档贡献指南和模板\n212:    - 举办文档编写培训和分享会\n213: \n214: ## Alternatives Considered\n215: \n216: ### Alternative 1: 仅维护代码注释和 README\n217: \n218: **描述**：仅依赖代码中的注释和项目根目录的 README.md 文件。\n219: \n220: **优点**：\n221: - 零额外开发成本\n222: - 文档紧贴代码，更新成本低\n223: - 简单直接\n224: \n225: **缺点**：\n226: - 不适合架构级别的文档\n227: - 缺少系统性的组织和导航\n228: - 不利于非技术人员理解\n229: - 无法提供丰富的示例和教程\n230: - 不支持版本管理和发布\n231: \n232: **决定**：不采纳。代码注释和 README 不足以支撑一个完整的技术文档体系。\n233: \n234: ### Alternative 2: 使用外部文档平台（如 Read the Docs）\n235: \n236: **描述**：使用第三方的文档托管平台进行文档管理和发布。\n237: \n238: **优点**：\n239: - 开箱即用的文档托管\n240: - 自动构建和部署\n241: - 支持搜索和版本管理\n242: - 社区活跃度高\n243: \n244: **缺点**：\n245: - 依赖第三方服务\n246: - 自定义能力有限\n247: - 可能存在数据安全顾虑\n248: - 网络访问限制\n249: - 集成成本较高\n250: \n251: **决定**：不采纳。内部文档系统提供更好的控制和集成能力。\n252: \n253: ### Alternative 3: 使用代码注释自动生成文档（如 GoDoc、Sphinx）\n254: \n255: **描述**：通过工具从代码注释中自动提取和生成文档。\n256: \n257: **优点**：\n258: - 文档与代码保持同步\n259: - 减少手动编写工作\n260: - 生成速度快\n261: \n262: **缺点**：\n263: - 不适合高层架构文档\n264: - 缺少非代码相关的文档（如部署、运维）\n265: - 生成的文档质量和可读性有限\n266: - 难以提供教程和最佳实践\n267: \n268: **决定**：部分采纳。对于 API 参考，可以结合自动生成工具，但架构和教程仍需手动编写。\n269: \n270: ### Alternative 4: 维护独立的 Wiki 系统\n271: \n272: **描述**：使用 Wiki 系统（如 Confluence、GitLab Wiki）进行文档管理。\n273: \n274: **优点**：\n275: - 易于编辑和协作\n276: - 支持丰富的多媒体内容\n277: - 灵活的组织结构\n278: \n279: **缺点**：\n280: - 缺少版本控制和代码集成\n281: - 文档质量难以保证\n282: - 搜索和导航体验较差\n283: - 不适合生成静态文档网站\n284: \n285: **决定**：不采纳。Wiki 不适合作为主要的技术文档系统，可用于补充性的快速笔记。\n286: \n287: ### Alternative 5: 使用静态站点生成器（如 Docusaurus、MkDocs）\n288: \n289: **描述**：使用现代化的静态站点生成器构建文档网站。\n290: \n291: **优点**：\n292: - 支持版本控制和代码集成\n293: - 优秀的搜索和导航体验\n294: - 可生成静态文件，易于部署\n295: - 支持自定义主题和插件\n296: - Markdown 友好，开发者易于上手\n297: - 社区活跃，生态丰富\n298: \n299: **缺点**：\n300: - 需要配置和初始搭建\n301: - 需要学习特定的工具和语法\n302: \n303: **决定**：采纳。这是当前最主流和成熟的技术文档解决方案，平衡了功能性、可维护性和开发者体验。\n304: \n305: ## Design Decisions\n306: \n307: ### 文档工具选择\n308: \n309: **选择**：Docusaurus\n310: \n311: **理由**：\n312: - 由 Facebook 开发，社区活跃，维护良好\n313: - 支持 Markdown 和 MDX，灵活性高\n314: - 内置搜索、版本控制、国际化等功能\n315: - 支持插件扩展\n316: - 现代化的 UI 设计，用户体验好\n317: - 易于部署到 GitHub Pages、Vercel 等平台\n318: \n319: **配置示例**：\n320: ```javascript\n321: // docusaurus.config.js\n322: module.exports = {\n323:   title: 'AgentCube Documentation',\n324:   tagline: 'Secure and scalable code execution platform',\n325:   url: 'https://docs.agentcube.io',\n326:   baseUrl: '/',\n327: \n328:   presets: [\n329:     [\n330:       '@docusaurus/preset-classic',\n331:       {\n332:         docs: {\n333:           sidebarPath: require.resolve('./sidebars.js'),\n334:           editUrl: 'https://github.com/agentcube/agentcube/edit/main/docs/',\n335:           versions: {\n336:             current: {\n337:               label: 'v1.0',\n338:               path: '/v1.0',\n339:             },\n340:           },\n341:         },\n342:         theme: {\n343:           customCss: require.resolve('./src/css/custom.css'),\n344:         },\n345:       },\n346:     ],\n347:   ],\n348: \n349:   themeConfig: {\n350:     navbar: {\n351:       title: 'AgentCube',\n352:       logo: {\n353:         alt: 'AgentCube Logo',\n354:         src: 'img/logo.svg',\n355:       },\n356:       items: [\n357:         {to: '/docs/introduction', label: '文档', position: 'left'},\n358:         {to: '/docs/api/overview', label: 'API', position: 'left'},\n359:         {\n360:           href: 'https://github.com/agentcube/agentcube',\n361:           label: 'GitHub',\n362:           position: 'right',\n363:         },\n364:       ],\n365:     },\n366:     footer: {\n367:       style: 'dark',\n368:       links: [\n369:         {\n370:           title: '文档',\n371:           items: [\n372:             {label: '入门指南', to: '/docs/introduction'},\n373:             {label: 'API 参考', to: '/docs/api'},\n374:           ],\n375:         },\n376:       ],\n377:     },\n378:   },\n379: };\n380: ```\n381: \n382: ### 文档组织结构\n383: \n384: **选择**：按受众和主题分层组织\n385: \n386: **理由**：\n387: - 不同用户（开发者、运维、最终用户）关注点不同\n388: - 主题分层便于导航和查找\n389: - 清晰的层次结构有助于文档维护\n390: \n391: **目录结构**：\n392: ```\n393: docs/\n394: ├── docs/\n395: │   ├── introduction/          # 入门指南\n396: │   │   ├── installation.md\n397: │   │   ├── quickstart.md\n398: │   │   └── concepts.md\n399: │   ├── architecture/          # 架构文档\n400: │   │   ├── overview.md\n401: │   │   ├── modules.md\n402: │   │   ├── data-flow.md\n403: │   │   ├── security.md\n404: │   │   └── observability.md\n405: │   ├── api/                   # API 文档\n406: │   │   ├── overview.md\n407: │   │   ├── rest.md\n408: │   │   ├── grpc.md\n409: │   │   ├── crd.md\n410: │   │   └── sdk.md\n411: │   ├── deployment/            # 部署文档\n412: │   │   ├── overview.md\n413: │   │   ├── kubernetes.md\n414: │   │   ├── docker.md\n415: │   │   └── configuration.md\n416: │   ├── operations/            # 运维文档\n417: │   │   ├── monitoring.md\n418: │   │   ├── logging.md\n419: │   │   ├── troubleshooting.md\n420: │   │   └── backup.md\n421: │   ├── tutorials/             # 教程\n422: │   │   ├── basic-usage.md\n423: │   │   ├── advanced-features.md\n424: │   │   └── integrations.md\n425: │   └── reference/             # 参考\n426: │       ├── configuration.md\n427: │       ├── cli-reference.md\n428: │       └── metrics.md\n429: ├── sidebars.js               # 侧边栏配置\n430: ├── docusaurus.config.js      # Docusaurus 配置\n431: └── static/                   # 静态资源\n432: ```\n433: \n434: ### API 文档生成策略\n435: \n436: **选择**：结合 OpenAPI/Swagger 规范和手动编写\n437: \n438: **理由**：\n439: - OpenAPI 规范可以自动生成交互式 API 文档\n440: - 手动编写可以提供更丰富的说明和示例\n441: - 两者结合可以兼顾准确性和易用性\n442: \n443: **实现方式**：\n444: 1. 为所有 REST API 定义 OpenAPI 规范文件（`docs/openapi.yaml`）\n445: 2. 使用 Docusaurus 的插件（如 `docusaurus-plugin-openapi`）渲染 API 文档\n446: 3. 在 API 文档中添加详细的描述、参数说明、示例代码\n447: 4. 为复杂场景提供额外的教程和最佳实践\n448: \n449: **OpenAPI 规范示例**：\n450: ```yaml\n451: openapi: 3.0.0\n452: info:\n453:   title: AgentCube API\n454:   version: 1.0.0\n455:   description: AgentCube platform REST API\n456: \n457: paths:\n458:   /v1/sessions/{namespace}/{kind}/{name}:\n459:     post:\n460:       summary: Create a new session\n461:       operationId: createSession\n462:       tags:\n463:         - Sessions\n464:       parameters:\n465:         - name: namespace\n466:           in: path\n467:           required: true\n468:           schema:\n469:             type: string\n470:         - name: kind\n471:           in: path\n472:           required: true\n473:           schema:\n474:             type: string\n475:             enum: [AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter]\n476:         - name: name\n477:           in: path\n478:           required: true\n479:           schema:\n480:             type: string\n481:       requestBody:\n482:         required: true\n483:         content:\n484:           application/json:\n485:             schema:\n486:               $ref: '#/components/schemas/CreateSessionRequest'\n487:       responses:\n488:         '201':\n489:           description: Session created successfully\n490:           content:\n491:             application/json:\n492:               schema:\n493:                 $ref: '#/components/schemas/Session'\n494: \n495: components:\n496:   schemas:\n497:     CreateSessionRequest:\n498:       type: object\n499:       properties:\n500:         timeout:\n501:           type: integer\n502:           description: Session timeout in seconds\n503:           default: 3600\n504:     Session:\n505:       type: object\n506:       properties:\n507:         session_id:\n508:           type: string\n509:           format: uuid\n510:         token:\n511:           type: string\n512:         sandbox_name:\n513:           type: string\n514:         expires_at:\n515:           type: string\n516:           format: date-time\n517: ```\n518: \n519: ### 文档版本管理\n520: \n521: **选择**：支持多版本文档（当前版本、旧版本、开发版本）\n522: \n523: **理由**：\n524: - 用户可能使用不同版本的 AgentCube\n525: - 需要保持历史文档的可用性\n526: - 开发中的新功能可以在开发版本中提前预览\n527: \n528: **实现方式**：\n529: 1. 使用 Docusaurus 的版本控制功能\n530: 2. 为每个主版本创建独立的文档分支\n531: 3. 在发布新版本时创建新的文档版本\n532: 4. 保留至少 2-3 个历史版本的文档\n533: \n534: **版本策略**：\n535: - **开发版本**：main 分支，包含最新的功能和文档\n536: - **当前版本**：最新稳定版（如 v1.0）\n537: - **历史版本**：过去的主要版本（如 v0.9）\n538: \n539: ### 文档审查和更新流程\n540: \n541: **选择**：将文档更新纳入代码审查流程\n542: \n543: **理由**：\n544: - 确保文档与代码同步更新\n545: - 提高文档质量\n546: - 建立文档维护意识\n547: \n548: **实现方式**：\n549: 1. 在 PR 模板中添加文档更新检查项\n550: 2. 对涉及 API 变更的 PR，要求同步更新文档\n551: 3. 定期（如每月）进行文档审计，检查过时内容\n552: 4. 建立文档贡献指南，明确文档编写规范\n553: \n554: **PR 模板示例**：\n555: ```markdown\n556: ## 变更类型\n557: - [ ] Bug 修复\n558: - [ ] 新功能\n559: - [ ] 功能改进\n560: - [ ] 文档更新\n561: \n562: ## 文档更新\n563: - [ ] 我已更新相关文档\n564: - [ ] 我已添加或更新 API 文档\n565: - [ ] 我已添加或更新示例代码\n566: ```\n567: \n568: ## Implementation Plan\n569: \n570: ### Phase 1: 基础设施搭建（Day 1-2）\n571: \n572: **目标**：建立文档站点和开发环境\n573: \n574: **任务**：\n575: 1. 初始化 Docusaurus 项目\n576: 2. 配置项目结构和主题\n577: 3. 设置 CI/CD 自动部署\n578: 4. 配置域名和 HTTPS\n579: 5. 编写文档贡献指南\n580: \n581: **交付物**：\n582: - 可访问的文档站点\n583: - 文档开发环境配置文档\n584: - 贡献指南\n585: \n586: ### Phase 2: 架构文档（Day 3-5）\n587: \n588: **目标**：完成核心架构文档\n589: \n590: **任务**：\n591: 1. 编写架构概览\n592: 2. 编写模块设计文档\n593: 3. 编写数据流文档\n594: 4. 编写安全架构文档\n595: 5. 编写可观测性文档\n596: 6. 添加架构图和流程图\n597: \n598: **交付物**：\n599: - 完整的架构文档\n600: - 架构图和流程图\n601: \n602: ### Phase 3: API 文档（Day 6-8）\n603: \n604: **目标**：完成 API 参考文档\n605: \n606: **任务**：\n607: 1. 编写 OpenAPI 规范\n608: 2. 配置 API 文档插件\n609: 3. 编写 REST API 文档\n610: 4. 编写 gRPC API 文档\n611: 5. 编写 CRD API 文档\n612: 6. 编写 SDK 参考文档\n613: 7. 添加代码示例\n614: \n615: **交付物**：\n616: - 完整的 API 参考文档\n617: - OpenAPI 规范文件\n618: - 交互式 API 文档\n619: \n620: ### Phase 4: 部署和运维文档（Day 9-10）\n621: \n622: **目标**：完成部署和运维指南\n623: \n624: **任务**：\n625: 1. 编写快速开始指南\n626: 2. 编写 Kubernetes 部署指南\n627: 3. 编写配置参考\n628: 4. 编写监控和告警指南\n629: 5. 编写故障排查指南\n630: 6. 编写备份和恢复指南\n631: \n632: **交付物**：\n633: - 完整的部署和运维文档\n634: - 配置示例\n635: - 故障排查清单\n636: \n637: ### Phase 5: 教程和示例（Day 11-12）\n638: \n639: **目标**：提供实用的教程和示例\n640: \n641: **任务**：\n642: 1. 编写基础教程\n643: 2. 编写高级用法教程\n644: 3. 编写集成示例\n645: 4. 编写最佳实践\n646: 5. 添加完整的代码示例\n647: \n648: **交付物**：\n649: - 多个教程文档\n650: - 代码示例库\n651: - 最佳实践指南\n652: \n653: ### Phase 6: 文档优化和发布（Day 13-14）\n654: \n655: **目标**：优化文档质量和用户体验\n656: \n657: **任务**：\n658: 1. 审查和编辑所有文档\n659: 2. 优化导航和搜索\n660: 3. 添加图表和插图\n661: 4. 配置版本管理\n662: 5. 配置国际化（可选）\n663: 6. 正式发布文档站点\n664: \n665: **交付物**：\n666: - 正式发布的文档站点\n667: - 文档维护流程文档\n668: \n669: ## Success Criteria\n670: \n671: 1. **文档完整性**\n672:    - 所有核心模块都有架构文档\n673:    - 所有公共 API 都有参考文档\n674:    - 提供完整的部署和运维指南\n675:    - 至少 5 个实用的教程\n676: \n677: 2. **文档质量**\n678:    - 所有文档通过拼写和语法检查\n679:    - 代码示例可以直接运行\n680:    - 架构图和流程图清晰准确\n681:    - 用户反馈满意度 > 80%\n682: \n683: 3. **可维护性**\n684:    - 文档更新流程已建立并执行\n685:    - CI/CD 自动部署正常工作\n686:    - 文档版本管理正常\n687:    - 贡献者可以轻松添加文档\n688: \n689: 4. **可用性**\n690:    - 文档站点加载速度 < 2s\n691:    - 搜索功能正常工作\n692:    - 导航结构清晰\n693:    - 支持移动设备访问\n694: \n695: 5. **社区反馈**\n696:    - GitHub issues 中文档相关问题减少 > 50%\n697:    - 收到至少 10 个正面反馈\n698:    - 至少 5 个外部贡献者提交文档改进\n699: \n700: ## Resources Required\n701: \n702: ### Engineering Resources\n703: \n704: | 角色 | 工时 | 职责 |\n705: |------|------|------|\n706: | 技术文档工程师 | 60-80 | 架构文档、API 文档编写 |\n707: | 开发工程师 | 40-60 | 技术内容审核、代码示例 |\n708: | 运维工程师 | 20-30 | 部署文档、运维指南 |\n709: | UI/UX 设计师 | 10-20 | 文档站点设计、图表制作 |\n710: | **总计** | **130-190** | |\n711: \n712: ### Infrastructure\n713: \n714: - **文档站点托管**：GitHub Pages、Vercel 或 Netlify\n715: - **CI/CD**：GitHub Actions 自动构建和部署\n716: - **域名**：docs.agentcube.io\n717: - **监控**：文档站点访问统计\n718: \n719: ### Tools and Dependencies\n720: \n721: | 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n722: |------|------|------|\n723: | Docusaurus | v3.x | 文档站点生成器 |\n724: | Node.js | 18+ | JavaScript 运行时 |\n725: | Mermaid | Latest | 图表生成 |\n726: | OpenAPI/Swagger | 3.0 | API 规范 |\n727: | Git | Latest | 版本控制 |\n728: \n729: ## Open Questions\n730: \n731: 1. **文档语言**：是否需要提供多语言支持（如中文、英文）？\n732:    - **当前计划**：优先完成英文文档，后续考虑添加中文支持\n733: \n734: 2. **文档版本保留策略**：保留多少个历史版本的文档？\n735:    - **当前计划**：保留当前版本和 2 个历史版本\n736: \n737: 3. **API 文档自动化**：是否需要从代码注释自动生成 API 文档？\n738:    - **当前计划**：主要使用 OpenAPI 规范，结合部分自动生成\n739: \n740: 4. **交互式示例**：是否需要在文档中嵌入可运行的代码示例？\n741:    - **当前计划**：使用 CodeSandbox 或 StackBlitz 集成简单的交互示例\n742: \n743: 5. **文档站点部署**：使用哪个平台部署文档站点？\n744:    - **当前计划**：使用 GitHub Pages（免费、稳定、集成良好）\n745: \n746: ## Approval\n747: \n748: - [ ] Tech Lead\n749: - [ ] Engineering Manager\n750: - [ ] Documentation Owner\n751: - [ ] QA/Testing Representative\n\n(End of file - total 751 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-043: 架构设计文档与 API 文档\n\n## Overview\n\n本提案旨在完善和增强 AgentCube 平台的架构设计文档与 API 文档，为开发者、运维人员和用户提供全面、准确、易于理解的技术文档。这将包括架构概览、模块设计、数据流、API 规范、部署指南等内容，并建立文档维护和更新机制。\n\n## Purpose\n\n为 AgentCube 平台建立完整、系统化的技术文档体系，实现以下目标：\n\n1. **知识传递与共享**：为团队成员提供统一的技术知识库，加速新成员上手\n2. **降低沟通成本**：通过详细的文档减少重复的技术问题解答\n3. **提升开发效率**：为 API 使用和系统集成提供清晰的参考\n4. **支持运维部署**：提供部署、配置、监控和故障排查指南\n5. **促进社区发展**：为开源社区提供高质量的用户和开发者文档\n6. **确保文档可持续性**：建立文档维护和更新流程\n\n## Module\n\n`docs`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775900803451,"end":1775900803477}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775900803483,"sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","part":{"id":"prt_d7befbeeb001G7Xfftd97j1jeZ","messageID":"msg_d7befa450001ubbKcqXmxEdqHw","sessionID":"ses_28410712dffe2YTvwM8OaDTSPJ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-84f935075cee4b6e99a4b09d256bb86a","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-043/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-043 — 架构设计文档与 API 文档 Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module**: `docs`\n4: **Language**: Markdown\n5: **Size**: M\n6: **Stage**: ST-3 completed\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Tasks\n11: \n12: ### T001: Docusaurus project initialization\n13: - [ ] Create `docs/` directory structure\n14: - [ ] Initialize Docusaurus with `npx create-docusaurus@latest docs classic`\n15: - [ ] Verify `package.json` contains Docusaurus dependencies\n16: - [ ] Verify `docusaurus.config.js` configuration file exists\n17: - [ ] Configure project title, tagline, URL, and baseUrl\n18: - [ ] Set up `sidebars.js` for navigation structure\n19: \n20: ### T002: Docusaurus configuration\n21: - [ ] Configure theme settings (navbar, footer)\n22: - [ ] Set up custom CSS in `src/css/custom.css`\n23: - [ ] Configure documentation plugin settings\n24: - [ ] Set up GitHub edit URL for \"Edit this page\" functionality\n25: - [ ] Configure version control settings\n26: - [ ] Add logo and favicon assets to `static/` directory\n27: \n28: ### T003: Documentation directory structure creation\n29: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/introduction/` directory\n30: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/` directory\n31: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/api/` directory\n32: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/deployment/` directory\n33: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/operations/` directory\n34: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/tutorials/` directory\n35: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/reference/` directory\n36: - [ ] Verify all directories exist with correct structure\n37: \n38: ### T004: Architecture overview documentation\n39: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/overview.md`\n40: - [ ] Add system architecture diagram (Mermaid or image)\n41: - [ ] Document core components (Router, WorkloadManager, PicoD, Controller Manager, Agentd)\n42: - [ ] Explain technology stack (Go, Python, Kubernetes, Redis)\n43: - [ ] Document design principles and architecture decisions\n44: - [ ] Add component interaction diagram\n45: \n46: ### T005: Router module documentation\n47: - [ ] Document Router module architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n48: - [ ] Explain session routing logic\n49: - [ ] Document connection management\n50: - [ ] Describe proxy behavior\n51: - [ ] Add Router component diagram\n52: - [ ] Document configuration options\n53: \n54: ### T006: Workload Manager module documentation\n55: - [ ] Document Workload Manager architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n56: - [ ] Explain resource allocation logic\n57: - [ ] Describe session lifecycle management\n58: - [ ] Document integration with Kubernetes API\n59: - [ ] Add Workload Manager component diagram\n60: - [ ] Document RBAC and permissions\n61: \n62: ### T007: Store module documentation\n63: - [ ] Document Store module architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n64: - [ ] Explain Redis/Valkey integration\n65: - [ ] Describe session data storage schema\n66: - [ ] Document cache strategies\n67: - [ ] Add Store component diagram\n68: - [ ] Document data consistency guarantees\n69: \n70: ### T008: PicoD module documentation\n71: - [ ] Document PicoD architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n72: - [ ] Explain sandbox management functionality\n73: - [ ] Describe SSH connection handling\n74: - [ ] Document permission controls\n75: - [ ] Add PicoD component diagram\n76: - [ ] Document security isolation mechanisms\n77: \n78: ### T009: Controller Manager module documentation\n79: - [ ] Document Controller Manager architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n80: - [ ] Explain Kubernetes controller patterns\n81: - [ ] Describe CRD reconciliation logic\n82: - [ ] Document event handling\n83: - [ ] Add Controller Manager component diagram\n84: - [ ] Document webhook configurations\n85: \n86: ### T010: Agentd module documentation\n87: - [ ] Document Agentd architecture in `docs/docs/architecture/modules.md`\n88: - [ ] Explain idle cleanup logic\n89: - [ ] Describe resource monitoring\n90: - [ ] Document cleanup policies\n91: - [ ] Add Agentd component diagram\n92: - [ ] Document scheduling and thresholds\n93: \n94: ### T011: Data flow documentation\n95: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/data-flow.md`\n96: - [ ] Document request processing flow (Client → Router → Workload Manager → Sandbox)\n97: - [ ] Add session lifecycle state machine\n98: - [ ] Document data flow diagrams for common operations\n99: - [ ] Explain state transitions\n100: - [ ] Document timeout and error handling flows\n101: \n102: ### T012: Security architecture documentation\n103: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/security.md`\n104: - [ ] Document authentication mechanisms (JWT, K8s TokenReview)\n105: - [ ] Explain authorization model (RBAC, permissions)\n106: - [ ] Describe network isolation strategies\n107: - [ ] Document resource isolation mechanisms\n108: - [ ] Explain data encryption (at rest and in transit)\n109: - [ ] Add security architecture diagram\n110: \n111: ### T013: Observability documentation\n112: - [ ] Create `docs/docs/architecture/observability.md`\n113: - [ ] Document monitoring metrics design\n114: - [ ] Define key performance indicators (KPIs)\n115: - [ ] Explain logging standards and formats\n116: - [ ] Document distributed tracing approach\n117: - [ ] Describe alerting strategies\n118: - [ ] Add observability stack diagram\n119: \n120: ### T014: API overview documentation\n121: - [ ]